entries.title: Oral Health Risks of Vaping
entries.content: The use of an e-cigarette is often called “vaping,” but “vaping” can also refer to a marijuana vaporizer pen. Learn more about what it is and how it damages both our oral and overall health.

entries.title: Quick Tips for Combating the Evils of Halloween Treats
entries.content: It can be difficult to manage the amount of candy that your child gets while out trick or treating. But you can manage the amount of candy that your child keeps. Click to find out solutions other than eating it yourself.
